<p>Other stars include Danielle Lloyd ($20), Megan Barton Hanson ($24.99), Lauren Goodger ($50), Chloe Khan ($19.99), Katie Salmon ($16), Courtney Stodden ($30),  and Ex On The Beach’s Leonie McSorley ($17). Former Big Brother star Bex Shiner's comes in at a bargain $4.99, while YouTuber Tana Mongeau and former WWE star Enzo Amore offer free subscriptions.</p>
